### ============================================================
### 미션 관리 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 생성
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning Exercise",
  "description": "30 minutes of morning exercise every day",
  "category": "HEALTH",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "endDate": "2025-01-31",
  "repeatType": "DAILY",
  "maxParticipants": 10
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 상세 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 미션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/my
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 공개 미션 목록 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/public?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드의 미션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/guild/guild-id-here
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수정
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Morning Exercise",
  "description": "45 minutes of morning exercise",
  "maxParticipants": 20
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 공개
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/open
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 시작
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/start
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 완료
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/complete
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 취소
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/cancel
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### 미션 참가자 관리 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 참가
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/join
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 참가자 수락 (미션 생성자용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/participants/1/accept
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 진행 시작
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/start-progress
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 진행률 업데이트
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/progress?progress=50
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 참가 완료
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/complete-participation
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 탈퇴
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/withdraw
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 참가자 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/participants
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 참가 정보 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/my-participation
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 미션 참가 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/my-participations
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### 미션 실행 추적 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 날짜 실행 완료 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/complete?note=Completed morning run
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 모든 실행 기록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 기간별 실행 기록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/range?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 오늘 실행해야 할 미션 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/executions/today
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 완료율 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/completion-rate
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
